.TH SHOAL-SANDBOX-EXEC 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-sandbox-exec \- run a process under a Shoal filesystem policy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-sandbox-exec
.RI [ \-\-read " path" ]
.RI [ \-\-write " path" ]
.RI [ \-\-delete " path" ]
.B \-\-
.I command
.RI [ args ...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Applies the requested filesystem sandbox and replaces itself with COMMAND.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal (1),
.BR shoal-kernel (1)
